name: Virtual Reality Parkour Castle
description: In virtual reality, what started as a differently intentioned 3D model sculpture changed when an anonymous young player entered the server, made themselves super tiny, and began climbing all over everything. Before long, I was busy drawing new tunnels and obstacles for this sentient, silent character to climb and jump through in real-time. Almost everything in this model was something they climbed on as a very very small person, 1/50th or 1/100th of the height of the whole structure.
